{"tid":2182042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加州500人full gear撐陳維明抗爭者雕塑  「港人爭取自由豐碑」揭幕","createTime":"2020-08-31T04:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T06:09:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd68811707197c2c8590541ad2e69ff11c49fbf","tid":2182042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/BIVRZORBI5DITMO2OIHHWY2XLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FBIVRZORBI5DITMO2OIHHWY2XLA%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr08eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=dbef3655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FBIVRZORBI5DITMO2OIHHWY2XLA%2F&h=c9606afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/BIVRZORBI5DITMO2OIHHWY2XLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n加州500人full gear撐陳維明抗爭者雕塑 <br />\n「港人爭取自由豐碑」揭幕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】旅美藝術家陳維明為香港抗爭者雕刻的塑像「光復香港 時代革命」在加州自由雕塑公園揭幕，本報記者現場直擊，有數百人出席典禮，不少參加者戴上黃色頭盔及身穿黑衣。去年7.1曾進入立法會會議廳的梁繼平、被港府以港版國安法通緝的美國公民朱牧民都有出席。朱牧民受訪時指，這一個雕像不僅代表過去一年的抗爭，更代表對將來的期許，「呢個雕刻今年未必能夠喺香港（出現），但我相信繼續抗爭落去，出年可以喺香港見」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：限武力 削撥款 賦權查  美制衡警暴完勝港府<br />\n<br />\n駐洛杉磯記者張紫茵/特約記者Alston<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3W8RngQKrOrERuLtzMLAQkvjtAg=/3150x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UP6G334T3ZAM3DOV37545WDPJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3W8RngQKrOrERuLtzMLAQkvjtAg%3D%2F3150x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUP6G334T3ZAM3DOV37545WDPJI.jpg&h=56d97125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■製作歷時五個月的香港抗爭者雕塑在加州揭幕，參加者戴上頭盔口罩身穿黑衣到場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/unjKdHGHlF6VDZCnYr08vmhkAys=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZDYP2ACJ7FH63NJ2VXW4F3V6CQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FunjKdHGHlF6VDZCnYr08vmhkAys%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZDYP2ACJ7FH63NJ2VXW4F3V6CQ.jpg&h=f8326be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳維明<br />\n<br />\n揭幕儀式在當地時間29日傍晚6時開始，由陳維明、梁繼平及六四民運人士王軍濤主禮。本報記者在自由雕塑公園現場所見，有約500人參加揭幕式，不少參加者戴上口罩、黃色頭盔及身穿黑衣，有人攜帶文宣及「光時旗」，一名「絲打」爬上雕塑插下旗幟，現場參加者又合唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n據知，「光復香港 時代革命」雕塑用了五個月時間製作，頂蓋仿照獅子山山形，四面刻有民主女神像，左右伴隨和、勇兩派，另有百萬人和平抗議和示威者衝擊立法會等反送中場面。對於出席人數比想像多一倍，陳維明表示非。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n朱牧民表示，雕像對香港人、對他都別具意義，因為這個雕像不只是表達過去一年的香港故事，也是為了將來的希望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e3Dj0xQuUg9ZU8iSnU3lcNbaPog=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6JBW5LWB6ZDEFDKQ5WK3GPPPUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe3Dj0xQuUg9ZU8iSnU3lcNbaPog%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6JBW5LWB6ZDEFDKQ5WK3GPPPUU.jpg&h=46a8a664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■公園設有連儂牆讓參觀者將心聲掛在鐵網。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oYDc6ZflAuteQYuxkJbr9g841G0=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WJW7V4I6DRDYPEJZ7FASHNPEYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoYDc6ZflAuteQYuxkJbr9g841G0%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWJW7V4I6DRDYPEJZ7FASHNPEYE.jpg&h=9f34b910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■雕塑上刻有示威者抗爭及防暴警舉槍畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱牧民：希望出年香港見<br />\n<br />\n朱牧民續指：「我喺美國住咗30幾年，呢個雕刻今年未必能夠喺香港（出現），我返唔到去。今年未必返到去，但我相信繼續抗爭落去，出年可以喺香港見。」<br />\n<br />\n梁繼平去年7.1在立法會發言一幕也被記錄在雕塑上，他指那一日對香港人。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n參與揭幕儀式的香港移民林先生表示感動，因從反送中開始到港版國安法的打壓都可在。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8bfc4e496fe9eb87a9020569ad57a9a144a3f6f1","tid":2182042,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fcf2150264e75e2a9d3a7e85da196b0dcb69adb6","tid":2182042,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"Very Nice"},{"pid":"d7a8960165c962f5be71cef1066652f5234616ed","tid":2182042,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07412756011bf0b77edb729e0e6f349692f0445","tid":2182042,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789e6bb57e2c78af4726447dedd8a81fb9d9f82f","tid":2182042,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c30b78db0984d127d6238f5ce60dacf01356dee","tid":2182042,"uid":70371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e34a0e3a9de1d6f7d0e6353c97999b0668ee75ea","